name: dt
description: The Date date

name: epoch
description: The epoch date

name: dayName
description: Day name (i.e., Monday, Tuesday...) of the date

name: dayOfWeek
description: ISO 8601 day of the week (Monday=1 to Sunday=7) of the date

name: dayOfMonth
description: ISO 8601 day of the month (starting with 1) of the date

name: dayOfQuarter
description: ISO 8601 day of the quarter (starting with 1) of the date

name: dayOfYear
description: ISO 8601 day of the year (starting with 1) of the date

name: weekOfMonth
description: ISO 8601 week of the month (starting with 1) of the date

name: weekOfYear
description: ISO 8601 week of the year (starting with 1) of the date

name: month
description: Month-truncated date.

name: monthOfYear
description: ISO 8601 month of the year (starting with 1) of the date

name: monthName
description: Month name (i.e., January, February...) of the date.

name: monthNameShort
description: Monday short name (i.e., Jan, Feb...) of the date.

name: quarterOfYear
description: ISO 8601 quarter of the year (starting with 1) of the date.

name: quarterName
description: Quarter name (i.e., Q1, Q2...) of the date.

name: year
description: ISO 8601 year (1.e., 2018) of the date.

name: mmyyyy
description: The mmyyyy printable version of a date.

name: mmddyyyy
description: The mmddyyyy printable version of a date.

name: yyyymmdd
description: The yyyymmdd sortable printable version of a date.

name: isWeekend
description: 1 if this is a weekend day, 0 otherwise.

name: isBusinessDay
description: 1 if this is a business day, 0 otherwise.

name: isHoliday
description: 1 if this is a holiday, 0 otherwise.

name: holidayName
description: The name of the holiday if applicable.

name: created
description: The timestamp for when the record was created. (TILDA.DateDim)

name: lastUpdated
description: The timestamp for when the record was last updated. (TILDA.DateDim)

name: deleted
description: The timestamp for when the record was deleted. (TILDA.DateDim)
